# ----- Input data MAPS (might be big bc its GIS)
# Ignore everything under data_in ...
data/data_in/**
# ...BUT Keep Markdown and PDF files anywhere inside data_in
# OKKIO:
# ------ `/**/*.md` matches Markdown files at ANY depth under data/data_in/
# ------ `/*.md` matches Markdown files at 1st level under data/data_in/
!data/data_in/**/*.md
# ex: `data/data_in/istat_shp_ITA_spiega.md`
!data/data_in/**/*.pdf
# Optional: keep the directory structure itself so Git doesn't drop empty dirs
!data/data_in/

# ----- IGNORE Derived data/exports (THE HEAVY ONES)
# Vector datasets (ESRI Shapefile family)
data/data_out/**/*.shp
